#: ../../platform/overview.rst:2
msgid "Platform Overview"
msgstr "平台概览"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:4
msgid ""
"DeePAW is an online inference service platform for the DeePAW method, "
"offering both a web interface and a RESTful API. It is designed to provide "
"materials science researchers with efficient, high-throughput charge density"
" calculation services."
msgstr ""
"DeePAW 是面向 DeePAW 方法的在线推理服务平台，同时提供 Web 界面与 RESTful "
"API。其设计目标是为材料科学研究者提供高效、高通量的电荷密度计算服务。"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:7
msgid "Core Features"
msgstr "核心功能"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:9
msgid ""
"**Batch charge density prediction**: Predicts three-dimensional charge "
"density distributions from atomic structure files"
msgstr "**批量电荷密度预测**：由原子结构文件预测三维电荷密度分布"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:10
msgid ""
"**Multi-format file support**: Supports 15 structure file formats including "
"CIF, VASP, XYZ, and PDB"
msgstr "**多格式文件支持**：支持 CIF、VASP、XYZ、PDB 在内的 15 种结构文件格式"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:11
msgid ""
"**Multi-GPU parallel scheduling**: Built-in priority queue and GPU task "
"scheduler supporting concurrent multi-task execution"
msgstr "**多 GPU 并行调度**：内置优先级队列与 GPU 任务调度器，支持多任务并发执行"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:12
msgid ""
"**RESTful API**: Comprehensive programmatic access interface for seamless "
"integration into automated workflows"
msgstr "**RESTful API**：提供完整的程序化访问接口，可无缝集成至自动化工作流"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:13
msgid ""
"**CHGCAR output**: VASP-compatible format, directly visualizable with tools "
"such as VESTA and Ovito"
msgstr "**CHGCAR 输出**：兼容 VASP 格式，可直接使用 VESTA、Ovito 等工具可视化"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:14
msgid ""
"**Real-time progress tracking**: Live task status updates delivered via "
"WebSocket"
msgstr "**实时进度跟踪**：通过 WebSocket 推送任务状态实时更新"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:15
msgid ""
"**Web frontend**: React-based interactive interface with 3D isosurface "
"visualization"
msgstr "**Web 前端**：基于 React 的交互式界面，支持三维等值面可视化"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:16
msgid ""
"**Model warm-start**: GPU model caching mechanism that keeps the model "
"resident in VRAM after the first inference, eliminating repeated loading "
"overhead for subsequent tasks"
msgstr "**模型预热启动**：GPU 模型缓存机制可在首次推理后将模型常驻于显存，消除后续任务的重复加载开销"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:19
msgid "Technology Stack"
msgstr "技术栈"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:21
msgid "**Frontend**: React 19 + TypeScript + Vite + Plotly.js"
msgstr "**前端**：React 19 + TypeScript + Vite + Plotly.js"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:22
msgid "**Backend**: FastAPI + Uvicorn (ASGI)"
msgstr "**后端**：FastAPI + Uvicorn（ASGI）"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:23
msgid "**Inference**: PyTorch + E3NN + ASE"
msgstr "**推理**：PyTorch + E3NN + ASE"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:24
msgid "**Data format**: Multiple formats -> ASE Database -> CHGCAR (VASP)"
msgstr "**数据格式**：多种格式 -> ASE Database -> CHGCAR（VASP）"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:27
msgid "System Architecture"
msgstr "系统架构"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:41
msgid "GPU Task Scheduling"
msgstr "GPU 任务调度"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:43
msgid ""
"One worker thread per GPU, with exclusive access enforced via "
"``threading.Lock``"
msgstr "每块 GPU 对应一个工作线程，并通过 ``threading.Lock`` 实现独占访问"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:44
msgid "Tasks are processed in order of a priority queue (PriorityQueue)"
msgstr "任务按优先级队列（PriorityQueue）顺序处理"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:45
msgid ""
"Model caching: the first task loads the model into GPU VRAM (~5-10 s); "
"subsequent tasks reuse the cached instance (<0.1 s overhead)"
msgstr "模型缓存：首个任务将模型加载至 GPU 显存（约 5-10 s）；后续任务复用缓存实例（额外开销 <0.1 s）"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:46
msgid ""
"One model instance cached per GPU, occupying approximately 2-4 GB of VRAM"
msgstr "每块 GPU 缓存一个模型实例，约占用 2-4 GB 显存"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:49
msgid "System Requirements"
msgstr "系统要求"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:52
msgid "Server Side"
msgstr "服务端"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:54
msgid "Python 3.10+"
msgstr "Python 3.10+"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:55
msgid "CUDA 11.8+ / 12.x"
msgstr "CUDA 11.8+ / 12.x"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:56
msgid "GPU: 8 GB+ VRAM (16 GB+ recommended)"
msgstr "GPU：8 GB+ 显存（推荐 16 GB+）"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:57
msgid "Disk: approximately 5-10 MB per CHGCAR file"
msgstr "磁盘：每个 CHGCAR 文件约 5-10 MB"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:58
msgid "Memory: 16 GB+ (32 GB+ recommended)"
msgstr "内存：16 GB+（推荐 32 GB+）"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:61
msgid "Client Side"
msgstr "客户端"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:63
msgid "Python 3.7+ (only the ``requests`` library required)"
msgstr "Python 3.7+（仅需 ``requests`` 库）"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:64
msgid "Or any programming language with HTTP request support"
msgstr "或任意支持 HTTP 请求的编程语言"

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:65
msgid "No GPU requirement"
msgstr "无 GPU 要求"
